    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>GQRX Client:
  Gqrx 2.2 &ndash; [<a href="http://gqrx.dk/download">http://gqrx.dk/download</a>]</p>

<p>GQRX Server:
  Software:</p>

<pre><code>Get:
  libusb-1.0.0-dev
  git clone git://git.osmocom.org/rtl-sdr.git
  cmake
 Do:
  cd rtl-sdr/
  mkdir build
  cd build
  cmake ../ -DINSTALL_UDEV_RULES=ON # On to allow privlages for non-root users
  make
  sudo make install
  sudo ldconfig
 Use:
   rtl_tcp -a 0.0.0.0
</code></pre>

<p>  Linux:</p>

<pre><code>  Raspbian Wheezy, Build July 26th, 2013. - http://downloads.raspberrypi.org/images/raspbian/2013-07-26-wheezy-raspbian/2013-07-26-wheezy-raspbian.zip
SSH:
    http://steve.dynedge.co.uk/2012/05/29/enabling-ssh-on-debian-raspberry-pi/
More:
</code></pre>

